Optimized_Coin_Change(coins, amount)

  Create an array DP of size (amount + 1)
  Initialize DP[0] = 0
  Fill all other DP entries with Infinity
  
  FOR i FROM 1 TO amount DO:
      FOR each coin in coins DO:
          IF coin <= i THEN
              DP[i] = MIN(DP[i], DP[i - coin] + 1)
 
 IF DP[amount] == Infinity THEN
     RETURN -1
 ELSE
     RETURN DP[amount]
